│ opt: llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/VPlan.cpp:258: llvm::Value* llvm::VPTransformState::get(llvm::VPValue*, bool): Assertion `(VF.isScalar() || Def->isLiveIn() || hasVectorValue(Def) ||                       │
│ !vputils::onlyFirstLaneUsed(Def) || (hasScalarValue(Def, VPLane(0)) && Data.VPV2Scalars[Def].size() == 1)) && "Trying to access a single scalar per part but has multiple scalars " "per part."' failed.       │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
